lead_paragraph: Matt Ryan threw for 344 yards and four touchdowns, leading the Atlanta Falcons to an easy 43-28 road win over the Tampa Bay Buccaneers in Florida on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Quarterback Ryan Shines as Falcons Thump Buccaneers 43-28
